item.description:
Join us for a tour of the Mashpee-Mashpee River Woodlands (C3C). Breakfast first at Panera Bread in Mashpee at 8:45M.

Trustees of Reservations map of the Mashpee River Reservation area.  More info about the Mashpee River Reservation.

Panera Bread is in Mashpee Commons at 8 Steeple St. (At Mashpee Rotary (intersection of Routes #151 and 28), head west on #28, take second entrance on right into Mashpee Commons.)

Activity:Hiking

Status:OPEN Wooded walk along Mashpee River. Directions to hike start: Take Orchard Rd. off Rte.28 to end. Turn R. then quick L onto Mashpee Neck Rd. Go 1.1 miles to Mashpee River Woodlands Pkg.Lot on R.   Meet at 9:45AM. 2hrs.

Date(s):April 25, 2013 (Thu)Location:Massachusetts, Cape Cod,  MA

Offered By:Southeastern MassachusettsLeader:Farley Lewis 
farlewis@comcast.net Registration is not required for this activity. However, you may wish to contact the AMC leader if you have any questions. Dogs are not allowed on AMC hikes.  More info on the AMC at www.outdoors.org
